headline: Garmin announces industry accolades for JL Audio home speaker lineup
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) is proud to announce that JL Audio®, a Garmin brand, received an Innovation Award for its Pavilion™ line of outdoor home speakers from Home Technology Specialists of America, Inc. (HTSA), a leading consumer electronics trade group. The award was presented at HTSA's 2024 Fall Conference and recognizes products that offer exceptional performance and quality in home technology.
